metadata.name: Founder #1
metadata.description: The Founders are the inquisitive, fearless people who reverse-engineered the Day Zero Relics (https://opensea.io/collection/seekers-day-zero) to create a portal to another world. Founders earn crypto passively, can construct a player hub anywhere on Earth to jumpstart their local Seekers gameplay community, collect free in-game item drops on the Flow blockchain, and join the elite Founder Guild to have a voice in the development of the NFT-powered augmented reality video game, https://seekersnft.io. The Founders' incredible technology has ushered in a new era of progress for humanity and given Seekers the tools they need to explore, survive, and thrive in this new world. Enriched by these efforts, the Founders enjoy a productive and lucrative existence, and embody the Seekers movement in the establishment of humanity beyond the portal. Learn more at https://discord.seekersnft.io
